Use LESS CSS preprocessor for easier style coding.
 less/*.less -> styles/*.css


Download:
 npm install less -g

Use from command line:
 cd .phrozn/less/
 lessc -x vilniusphp.less ../styles/vilniusphp.css

Configure PHPStorm File Watcher:
  Program: lessc
  Arguments: -x --no-color $FileName$
  Working directory: $FileDir$
  Output path: ../styles/$FileNameWithoutExtension$.css
